Metadata.title: ScratchAid
Metadata.description: ScratchAid is a dedicated helpdesk service that allows Scratch users to easily manage bug reports and questions related to their projects. By incorporating features similar to GitHub Issues, it provides a platform for visualizing, tracking, and efficiently resolving problems that arise in projects.
